  "elapsed_s": 12.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he has an electrical appliance store and was the only electrician in [NON-ENGLISH], a town of about 20,000, so they spared him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was going in-- in-- into Budapest, and-- and on a Sunday night when they-- they called it a work train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They-- they were outside workers-- went back to the-- back to the city to work-- to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he-- he led me in there right to the-- right to the-- the-- the custom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, and everything in Budapest-- and then, we were working on the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this [INAUDIBLE] there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we came to the-- he came to a-- a hotel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he just whispered well, goodbye.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he kept walking, and I went into the hotel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was about 4 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had to-- to go to sleep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I-- I was in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Usually, [INAUDIBLE] fed us breakfast and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember, you had this where to go and a name, address and name, your first contact.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Sure enough, in-- in about two hours time, working, I went and inquired-- inquired policeman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So it's-- it's just to sort of-- see it-- it's a cover.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If you go to police-- minority, you must be [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, I him about the direction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- and I came to the-- came to the-- the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I found the house and knocked on the door.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a lady, about-- about your height, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And opened door.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I gave her a password-- [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Robert. ?] And she froze.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She really got a shock, say-- saying his name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said, well lady, let's-- let's not waste any time, and just pushed her in, pushed her in-- right in the chest-- let's go inside.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
